# Public Supabase config for the cockpit frontend.
# Vite inlines VITE_* values into the browser bundle at build time, so these
# are NOT secrets — the anon key is a public client-side key and every visitor's
# browser already receives it. All data is protected by row-level security.
# Tracked in git on purpose so any build (Railway, CI, local) is self-contained.
